#: ../../source/support.rst:2
msgid "Support"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/support.rst:4
msgid "Nest is an MIT-licensed open source project with its ongoing development made possible thanks to the support by the community. This framework is a result of the long road, full of sleepless nights, working **after hours**, and busy weekends."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/support.rst:10
msgid "How can you help?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/support.rst:12
msgid "Nest doesn’t have a large company that sits behind and is continuously paying for hours spent on the development. I fully rely on the **goodness** ❤️ of the people. However, I would love to make this framework even more **powerful**, to be fully focused on delivering you great solutions that make coding process enjoyable: In order to help me, I run few supporting platforms:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/support.rst:19
msgid "become a backer or sponsor on `OpenCollective <https://opencollective.com/nest>`__"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/support.rst:21
msgid "use `PayPal <https://paypal.me/kamilmysliwiec>`__ to send a one-time donation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/support.rst:23
msgid "or reach me directly: mail@kamilmysliwiec.com"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/support.rst:25
msgid "If you fell in love with Nest, or you run a business which is using Nest, consider sponsoring its development to ensure that the project which your product relies on is **actively maintained** and improved. Also, your support could help me to work more on content that benefits whole Nest community, writing either educational blog posts or recording videos."
msgstr ""

